{"tid":1311114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"上水支線副本成就列表","createTime":"2019-07-13T04:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:22:48.000Z","uid":91659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc097abcab4bfffc112f932ef9bbad28f5dd3085","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲僅記勿忘初衷，身體力行，用智慧去夢遊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔再係淨係識一味鳩行，然後散水嘅新手，每次發夢都要了解背後嘅動機，以及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">期待帶黎嘅效果同日後影響</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以以下有幾點成就希望各位手足可以達成，時時銘記於心！<br />\n<br />\n是日主要成就 ： <br />\n<br />\n1. 大力宣傳五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n2. 在沒有人受傷/被捉嘅情況下完成副本<br />\n<br />\n3. 響應主題，打擊水貨走私行為，爭取反水貨市民支持<br />\n<br />\n次級成就<br />\n<br />\n1. 使用連儂牆攻勢，向街坊表達鮮明的民意取向<br />\n<br />\n2. 向內地旅客積極但和平地輸出革命，醞釀日後支爆嘅條件<br />\n<br />\n3. 親身評估當區黃藍比率，為區議會選舉做好準備<br />\n<br />\n4. 宣傳社會信用系統嘅禍害<br />\n<br />\n5. 向身體手足傳播正能量，抗爭先可以有動力繼續落去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBe water my friend, we are making history !!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffd3822c7b4957e144fb506c7e2ca6d59dfd314","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到有人理先"},{"pid":"979ada54c5ad85d1ce59a7d86e8b8a45978ef628","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e1a42182901a52aca9d20f2131f80f34c8dd1a08","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"68c87ad18ac7ac09cf6acb6f7385264f1e4e15c4","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"caaf32a7d62e6e524f2ff0a2a0a1111d46f935f8","tid":1311114,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"